<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l23">Lieben <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> vns hat
                        fürgelegt C Erber vnſer <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> / vvie daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l24">Er vnſicher ſeÿ voꝛ lyenhart
