<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> / <expan>Rog<ex>amus</ex></expan> daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l26">Jr denſelben <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> daran vveiſen <add><ab facs="#facs_68_r1l25">wollet </ab></add> / daʒ er den
