</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_68" id="32v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu <expan>Peͣrchenge<ex>n</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieben <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat fürgelegt <expan cert="unknown">C.</expan> Erber, unser
                            <expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie daz er unsicher sey vor
                        Lyenhart <expan>Sneid<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>. <expan>Rog<ex>amus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                        denselben <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> daran weisen <add>wollet</add>, daz er den
                                <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, sicher auf frewntlich recht. Das wöllen wir
                        etc. Und het dann <add><expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan></add>
<expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan>, czu dem unsern icht czu
                                <expan>spreche<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir im <add><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> aber
                                    <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbote<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>mit <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gewalt</add>
<expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogens</expan></add> slewnigs
                                <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> gern helffen, wenn wir des ermant
                        werden, so <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>obg<ex>enante</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, anheim ist; und laszt uns des
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> antwurt
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> wiszen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>a</ex>to</expan> ante
                            <expan>d<ex>o</ex>m<ex>ini</ex>cam</expan>
<expan>Trinitat<ex>is</ex></expan> anno <expan>oct<ex>av</ex>o</expan>.</ab>
</div>
